column1: Weekly search interest in all Brazil's presidential candidates along 2018. Search interest indexed to each candidate individually, from 0 to 100, where 100 means the highest search interest and 0 means the lowest or that there has not been enough data. Use this table if you'd like to see individual spikes in each candidate. To see how they conpare to each other, check table https://github.com/GoogleTrends/data/blob/master/Brazil_Presidential_Candidates_2018_Compared.csv
